SWNavigationMode.PreferenceItem.Name: Mouse Control
SWNavigationMode.PreferenceItem.desc:
Select the way you manipulate 3D views with your mouse in 3D viewing and modeling apps.

3DEXPERIENCE is recommended for most users because it has simple ways to rotate and zoom, combined with CATIA gestures for advanced users.

The other options use the mouse control familiar to CATIA and SOLIDWORKS users.
